long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
AI Quiz Generator is a Chrome extension that can generate quizzes for any website with AI.
Just open the sidepanel when you are visiting a website, click on the generate button, and then it will generate quizzes about the website content to let you test yourself.
